14n ≡ 46 mod 50`, but `46 ≡ 46 mod 50`, not `23`. \n\nSo earlier, when reducing modulo 25, we had `14n ≡ 21 mod 25` because `46 ≡ 21 mod 25`. \n\nBut modulo 50, `1",
